#Energy consumption - production
Glass
- energy 1kg: 2kWh (recycled 1kWh)
Paper
- energy 1kg: 3kWh
Steel
- energy 1kg: 5kWh (recycled 3kWh)
Plastics
- energy 1kg: 20kWh (recycled 10-15kWh)
Aluminium
- energy 1kg: 50kWh (recycled 5kWh)

